don't have best friends.

14:02.667 --> 14:04.408
Unless it's a dog.

14:04.452 --> 14:06.149
We're being raised
by a 10-year-old.

14:08.412 --> 14:10.719
<i>I had broken</i> <i>
my best friend's heart,</i>

14:10.762 --> 14:12.764
<i>but I knew I could fix it.</i>

14:15.202 --> 14:17.030
Oh -- Oh, hey.
Hey, have you seen Charlie?

14:18.248 --> 14:21.034
You know, I-I wanted
to apologize and, uh,

14:21.077 --> 14:24.037
let him know that I'm honored
to be his best man.

14:24.080 --> 14:27.301
Yeah, uh, it's a little late
for that, Dad.

14:27.344 --> 14:30.304
Uh, Charlie asked me
to be his best man.

14:30.347 --> 14:32.915
What?
And his lawyer.

14:32.959 --> 14:36.092
Told him not to let me handle
the prenup negotiations.

14:37.311 --> 14:38.268
Huh?

14:41.532 --> 14:43.273
