since Vivica banned me.

16:03.397 --> 16:06.008
And can you believe she put
my picture in every entrance?

16:06.052 --> 16:08.271
Like anyone could keep me
from missing this train wreck.

16:08.315 --> 16:10.012
Why you over here
looking all sad?

